title: Flaco the owl from Central Park
content:
Flaco an owl from Central Park

Flaco is an owl who escaped from the cage in Central park Zoo. NowhelivesinCentralpark in New York City. He became a celebrity for New Yorkers

Flaco is an owl who escaped the cage in Central park Zoo. He managed to learn and get skills necessarytoserviveinthe wild nature. Now he lives in Central park in New York City. He became a celebrity for New Yorkers.
